&lt;p&gt;The Trust’s Health Informatics Department is at the leading edge of clinical quality measurement in the NHS; incorporating new reporting, analytical systems and methodologies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Post holder will work closely with Informatics colleagues to deliver on mandated reporting requirements and to provide ad hoc reports to the organisation. This role is based at Yardley Court, Edgbaston.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic individual with drive and commitment. Applicants must have experience in SQL, manipulating large datasets and have good communication, interpersonal and organisational skills. The individual should be a logical thinker and have a keen eye for detail.&lt;/p&gt;
